27
00:02:09,500 --> 00:02:13,340
Mediator then dispatch this object to the appropriate handler.

28
00:02:14,510 --> 00:02:20,270
So if you look at the mediator pattern and pipeline behaviors, the mediator pattern is implemented

29
00:02:20,270 --> 00:02:20,570
by.

