00:02:20,570 --> 00:02:27,680
The mediator library is particularly useful in a complex or enterprise level applications, where request

31
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:31,070
processing often involves more than just business logic.

32
00:02:31,490 --> 00:02:38,210
In this kind of applications, handling a request might require additional steps like logging, validation,

33
00:02:38,210 --> 00:02:40,790
